oh, btw to those who are curious of knowing how to seed:
1. Leave your torrent client on
2. Play/Start your torrent from your client and leave it. (Even when you're done downloading, please don't STOP or REMOVE from your list)
Usually, it will say that it is seeding. Seeding can be done while you are downloading and even when you are finished downloading.

To those who are generous in helping us download: you can increase the upload rate from your preference, which will help us download it more efficiently. Cheers to those who are helping.
